  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK23">
<l>irumai vakaiterin tīṇṭaṟam pūṇṭār</l>
<l>perumai piṟaṅkiṟ ṟulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The greatness of those who have understood the two states, and in this life</l>
<l>have taken on dharma, is the [one] exalted thing in the world.</l>
<l>(Alternative understanding not suggested by commentators:</l>
<l>"By the greatness of those who have understood the two states, and in this</l>
<l>life have taken on dharma, the world is uplifted.")</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
